# Frontend

## Scope

- Contracts: `frontend/docs/api_contracts.md`
- Zod schemas: `frontend/src/lib/schemas/`
- API clients: `frontend/src/features/*/api/`

## Rules

- Validate API responses with Zod; treat contract violations as bugs.
- Use `VITE_API_URL` from env; prefer a single shared base URL config.
- Rankings and stats consume real API endpoints — no fixture-only public routes.
- Run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` after substantive changes.

## Verify

```bash
cd frontend && npm run lint && npm run build
```
